properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 16 at 1:49AM EST until January 18 at 4:00AM EST by NWS Jacksonville FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northeast winds increasing to 20 to 25 kt with a few gale
force gusts up to 35 kt and seas building to 6 to 10 feet.

* WHERE...All Southeast Georgia and Northeast Florida coastal
waters from Altamaha Sound GA to Flagler Beach FL out to 60 NM.

* WHEN...From 7 PM this evening to 4 AM EST Saturday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 7 PM THIS EVENING TO 4 AM EST SATURDAY
